<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Parcel Delivered Successfully</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: #2d3748;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            border-top: 4px solid #10b981;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .success-icon {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            background-color: #10b981;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .success-icon::after {
            content: 'âœ“';
            color: white;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #1a202c;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .tracking-number {
            background-color: #f7fafc;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3182ce;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .delivery-details {
            background-color: #f0fff4;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid #c6f6d5;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #4a5568;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #2d3748;
            text-align: right;
            max-width: 60%;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3182ce, #2c5aa0);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(49, 130, 206, 0.3);
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(49, 130, 206, 0.4);
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #718096;
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .support-info {
            background-color: #fef5e7;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 25px;
            border-left: 4px solid #f6ad55;
        }
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            body { padding: 10px; }
            .container { padding: 25px; }
            .detail-row { flex-direction: column; }
            .detail-value { text-align: left; margin-top: 5px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <div class="success-icon"></div>
        <h1>Package Delivered!</h1>
    </div>

    <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>

    <p>Great news! Your package has been successfully delivered. ðŸ“¦âœ…</p>

    <div class="tracking-number">
        Tracking Number: <%= trackingNumber %>
    </div>

    <div class="delivery-details">
        <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Delivery Address:</span>
            <span class="detail-value"><%= address %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Delivery Time:</span>
            <span class="detail-value"><%= deliveryTime %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Status:</span>
            <span class="detail-value" style="color: #10b981; font-weight: 600;">âœ“ Delivered</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= trackingUrl %>" class="button">View Delivery Details</a>
    </div>

    <p>Thank you for choosing <%= appName %> for your shipping needs. We hope to serve you again soon!</p>

    <div class="support-info">
        <strong>Need Help?</strong><br>
        If you have any questions about your delivery, please contact our support team at
        <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>" style="color: #d69e2e;"><%= supportEmail %></a>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.<br>
    This email was sent regarding tracking number <%= trackingNumber %>
</div>
</body>
</html>